-- Citi names Edward Kelly CFO
-- 
-- Fri Mar 20, 2009 8:07am EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2009/03/20/us-citi-cfo-idUSTRE52J2QM20090320

 

 (Reuters) - Citigroup Inc ( C.N ) on Friday announced Edward Kelly CFO. 

 Highlights: * Announces senior management changes * Says Gary Crittenden, previously CFO, named to the newly created role of chairman of Citi Holdings * Says Edward "Ned" Kelly, previously head of global banking, will assume the role of CFO at Citigroup